caption.title: Main components identified by GC-MS from essential oils of Nectandra megapotamica.

fn.p: All individuals were identified as Nectandra megapotamica, but from different regions. From the state of Mato Grosso do Sul: C1 to C3: city of Campo Grande; M1: city of Maracaju; P1 and P2: city of Ponta Porã. State of São Paulo: S1 to S5: city of São Paulo. n: number; RI: retention index of the compound; RIL: retention index of literature. The major compounds of each species are in bold.
